dialogueText: Mission Control to NANO@ do you read me?
We've lots to cover@ and time is not on our side.
Head east for now@ the facility's system are still active.
Stay sharp and conserve your battery—we need you operational.
Well@ well… look who we have here. A visitor.
I didn’t think anyone had the nerve to return.
Ignore him@ NANO. You’re doing great.
Just stay focused on the mission.
Be careful NANO@ we haven’t seen this before.
